<font color=#FFFF00>in making the world a better place.</font>

88
00:05:21,618 --> 00:05:23,534
<font color=#FFFF00>Please say a few words before we wrap up.</font>

89
00:05:23,558 --> 00:05:24,588
<font color=#FFFF00>First of all,</font>

90
