<font color=#FFFF00>I would like to show my gratitude to...</font>

91
00:05:28,148 --> 00:05:30,718
<font color=#FFFF00>the members of my party who trust in me.</font>

92
00:05:31,648 --> 00:05:32,848
<font color=#FFFF00>From now on,</font>

93
00:05:33,988 --> 00:05:37,424
<font color=#FFFF00>my dear and respectful citizens,</font>

94
