<font color=#FFFF00>I am Han Seong Sik from Minjeong Party.</font>

110
00:06:27,048 --> 00:06:28,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Who is that?</font>

111
00:06:29,048 --> 00:06:31,324
<font color=#FFFF00>- Isn't it my dear Seong Sik?
