113
00:06:35,488 --> 00:06:36,694
<font color=#FFFF00>That is him.</font>

114
00:06:36,718 --> 00:06:38,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Why is he saying hello to people?</font>

115
00:06:39,318 --> 00:06:41,217
<font color=#FFFF00>He went to the market.</font>

116
00:06:41,218 --> 00:06:42,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did he go?</font>

117
00:06:43,148 --> 00:06:45,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Did his mother want him
