120
00:06:53,088 --> 00:06:54,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Is your grandson running for...</font>

121
00:06:55,348 --> 00:06:57,617
<font color=#FFFF00>a seat in the National Assembly?</font>

122
00:06:57,618 --> 00:06:58,648
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

123
00:06:59,518 --> 00:07:00,948
<font color=#FFFF00>A seat in the National Assembly?</font>

124
00:07:03,018 --> 00:07:05,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Ae. Hyung Seop.</font>

125
00:07:06,118 --> 00:07:08,238
<font color=#FFFF00>Did Seong Sik mention that
