<font color=#FFFF00>It's 80 dollars.</font>

144
00:08:18,048 --> 00:08:20,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it 80 dollars?</font>

145
00:08:21,488 --> 00:08:22,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Wait a second.</font>

146
