00:08:33,018 --> 00:08:34,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Seriously.</font>

149
00:08:37,348 --> 00:08:39,387
<font color=#FFFF00>This is unbelievable.</font>

150
00:08:39,388 --> 00:08:40,948
<font color=#FFFF00>I am sorry. Please wait a moment.</font>

151
