<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook, I need you...</font>

153
00:08:46,518 --> 00:08:49,248
<font color=#FFFF00>to pay for mine today.</font>

154
00:08:49,658 --> 00:08:52,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother, this isn't good.</font>

155
00:08:53,048 --> 00:08:54,048
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it?</font>

156
00:08:54,488 --> 00:08:56,848
<font color=#FFFF00>I forgot to bring my wallet...</font>

157
00:08:57,118 --> 00:08:59,818
<font color=#FFFF00>again today.</font>

158
00:09:00,548 --> 00:09:01,658
<font color=#FFFF00>Dear me.</font>

159
00:09:04,318 --> 00:09:05,318
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

160
00:09:13,188 --> 00:09:15,588
<font color=#FFFF00>I apologize, Mother.</font>

161
00:09:17,548 --> 00:09:19,788
<font color=#FFFF00>What's gotten into you?
You're not as old as I am.</font>

162
00:09:20,158 --> 00:09:22,788
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe you forget
your wallet so many times.</font>

163
00:09:23,158 --> 00:09:26,164
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother, actually, I used this same bag...</font>

164
00:09:26,188 --> 00:09:28,664
<font color=#FFFF00>the other day I came here with you,</font>

165
00:09:28,688 --> 00:09:30,969
<font color=#FFFF00>and I forgot to put my wallet
