166
00:09:31,218 --> 00:09:34,188
<font color=#FFFF00>I should've remembered to bring it today.</font>

167
00:09:34,988 --> 00:09:36,788
<font color=#FFFF00>- I'm so sorry.
- Goodness.</font>

168
00:09:42,048 --> 00:09:43,848
<font color=#FFFF00>Mother, Father is here.</font>

169
00:09:44,618 --> 00:09:45,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Father, we are here!</font>

170
00:09:46,748 --> 00:09:47,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Hee Sook.</font>

171
00:09:48,948 --> 00:09:51,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you here? I called
