189
00:11:03,388 --> 00:11:05,988
<font color=#FFFF00>again at the market again today.</font>

190
00:11:06,418 --> 00:11:08,317
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it.</font>

191
00:11:08,318 --> 00:11:11,918
<font color=#FFFF00>I told you Hee Sook is too
