<font color=#FFFF00>Dad, don't worry too much.</font>

203
00:11:47,418 --> 00:11:50,488
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll visit his office right
away and talk to him.</font>

204
00:11:50,888 --> 00:11:53,288
<font color=#FFFF00>It might ruin our whole family.</font>

205
00:11:53,648 --> 00:11:55,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell him to give up now.</font>

206
00:11:55,648 --> 00:11:57,788
<font color=#FFFF00>I will. I'll call you later.</font>

207
00:12:01,388 --> 00:12:02,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Seriously.</font>

208
00:12:08,188 --> 00:12:09,988
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with him?</font>

209
00:12:10,318 --> 00:12:13,648
<font color=#FFFF00>(Han Seong Sik, Minjeong
Party's official candidate)</font>

210
00:12:17,088 --> 00:12:18,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Excuse me.</font>

211
00:12:19,648 --> 00:12:20,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello.</font>

212
00:12:24,118 --> 00:12:26,048
<font color=#FFFF00>What will you do?</font>

213
00:12:26,388 --> 00:12:28,948
<font color=#FFFF00>I need you to resolve it.</font>

214
00:12:33,518 --> 00:12:36,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon, did you talk to Seong Sik?</font>

215
00:12:36,888 --> 00:12:39,887
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello. I told you we'd meet again.</font>

216
00:12:39,888 --> 00:12:42,517
<font color=#FFFF00>How dare you come here?</font>

217
00:12:42,518 --> 00:12:44,218
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dad.
- Get up already.</font>

218
00:12:44,718 --> 00:12:46,718
<font color=#FFFF00>- What do you think you're doing?
- Dad.</font>

219
00:12:47,148 --> 00:12:48,848
<font color=#FFFF00>Stay out of this.</font>

220
00:12:49,188 --> 00:12:51,818
<font color=#FFFF00>- Get out of here.
- Goodness.</font>

221
00:12:52,788 --> 00:12:54,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

222
00:12:54,918 --> 00:12:56,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't ever come back again.</font>

223
00:12:57,148 --> 00:12:59,618
<font color=#FFFF00>If you come here again,
I'll call the police.</font>

224
00:13:00,118 --> 00:13:02,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Sure. Go ahead.</font>

225
00:13:02,188 --> 00:13:03,888
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't believe you just said that.</font>

226
00:13:04,018 --> 00:13:06,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Get lost now.</font>

227
00:13:07,818 --> 00:13:09,688
<font color=#FFFF00>I will leave now,</font>

228
00:13:09,788 --> 00:13:11,518
<font color=#FFFF00>but I'm coming back.</font>

229
00:13:13,148 --> 00:13:15,988
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll make sure to come back soon.
Wait for me.</font>

230
00:13:18,718 --> 00:13:20,618
<font color=#FFFF00>What a wench.</font>

231
00:13:23,318 --> 00:13:24,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad.</font>

232
00:13:32,988 --> 00:13:34,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Dad,</font>

233
00:13:35,648 --> 00:13:38,348
<font color=#FFFF00>you need to tell me so that I can help you.</font>

234
00:13:43,788 --> 00:13:45,288
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm afraid to tell you...</font>

235
00:13:46,418 --> 00:13:49,818
<font color=#FFFF00>that I don't want anything that
breaks Mom's heart to happen again.</font>

236
00:13:52,588 --> 00:13:55,788
<font color=#FFFF00>If she's Seong Joon's biological mother,</font>

237
00:13:56,888 --> 00:13:59,888
<font color=#FFFF00>please just give her what she
wants and let her walk away...</font>

238
00:14:00,088 --> 00:14:02,718
<font color=#FFFF00>for Mom's sake.</font>

239
00:14:04,988 --> 00:14:07,147
<font color=#FFFF00>Please don't just keep sighing.</font>

240
00:14:07,148 --> 00:14:09,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom shouldn't find this out.</font>

241
00:14:10,418 --> 00:14:13,518
<font color=#FFFF00>It took 10 years for her to
accept Seong Joon as her son.</font>

242
00:14:13,948 --> 00:14:17,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon came to us when he was seven,</font>

243
00:14:17,588 --> 00:14:20,118
<font color=#FFFF00>and she first hugged him when he turned 17.</font>

244
00:14:20,848 --> 00:14:23,748
<font color=#FFFF00>- This will perturb her again.
- Seong Hoon.</font>

245
00:14:27,188 --> 00:14:28,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes, Dad.</font>

246
00:14:28,948 --> 00:14:31,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Can you just help me...</font>

247
00:14:34,888 --> 00:14:37,418
<font color=#FFFF00>without asking anything?</font>

248
00:14:49,818 --> 00:14:50,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo!</font>

249
00:14:52,918 --> 00:14:54,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you here?</font>

250
00:14:55,388 --> 00:14:58,348
<font color=#FFFF00>When did you come back?
Will you stay here, then?</font>

251
00:14:59,148 --> 00:15:03,148
<font color=#FFFF00>You didn't come back because
you forgot something, right?</font>

252
00:15:03,288 --> 00:15:06,118
<font color=#FFFF00>You'll stay here forever, won't you?</font>

253
00:15:09,288 --> 00:15:12,618
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm so glad you are back.</font>

254
00:15:14,418 --> 00:15:16,888
<font color=#FFFF00>I also have good news.</font>

255
00:15:17,618 --> 00:15:20,848
<font color=#FFFF00>My dad is back. He said
he'll live in Korea.</font>

256
00:15:26,888 --> 00:15:29,748
<font color=#FFFF00>I returned to take care of a few things.</font>

257
00:15:30,418 --> 00:15:32,848
<font color=#FFFF00>I will leave again soon. Please go.</font>

258
00:15:34,318 --> 00:15:35,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo.</font>

259
00:15:36,318 --> 00:15:38,648
<font color=#FFFF00>- What's the matter?
- I need you to leave now.</font>

260
00:15:39,188 --> 00:15:42,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Nothing will change even if
I came back permanently.</font>

261
00:15:43,288 --> 00:15:44,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Now leave.</font>

262
00:15:46,488 --> 00:15:47,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Hold on.</font>

263
00:15:49,348 --> 00:15:52,288
<font color=#FFFF00>- Did something happen to you?
- Nothing happened.</font>

264
00:15:53,288 --> 00:15:54,688
<font color=#FFFF00>We're not together anymore.</font>

265
00:15:54,918 --> 00:15:58,017
<font color=#FFFF00>You also said we are finished...</font>

266
00:15:58,018 --> 00:15:59,858
<font color=#FFFF00>and you'll blame me for
the rest of your life.</font>

267
00:16:00,848 --> 00:16:02,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Do as you said.</font>

268
00:16:03,648 --> 00:16:04,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't try to find me.</font>

269
00:16:09,118 --> 00:16:10,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo.</font>

270
00:16:30,988 --> 00:16:33,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello, Mr. Lee. How are you?</font>

271
00:16:35,948 --> 00:16:37,648
<font color=#FFFF00>- Hello.
- Why don't you go inside?</font>

272
00:16:41,988 --> 00:16:43,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodbye.</font>

273
00:16:48,588 --> 00:16:51,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Get out. Leave already.</font>

274
00:16:51,588 --> 00:16:53,148
<font color=#FFFF00>That's enough, Mr. Kim.</font>

275
00:16:53,688 --> 00:16:56,848
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you joking with me? Do you
think anyone can be a writer?</font>

276
00:16:57,618 --> 00:17:00,018
<font color=#FFFF00>- I'm sorry.
- Dong Hui,</font>

277
00:17:00,318 --> 00:17:02,018
<font color=#FFFF00>sorry doesn't cut it.</font>

278
00:17:02,188 --> 00:17:06,294
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know we had to do extra
work while you were away?</font>

279
00:17:06,318 --> 00:17:08,547
<font color=#FFFF00>I made coffee for others and
even had to clean the office.</font>

280
00:17:08,548 --> 00:17:11,288
<font color=#FFFF00>That's enough, everyone.
She's here after all.</font>

281
00:17:11,788 --> 00:17:14,187
<font color=#FFFF00>It's good you mentioned it.
Why are you back?</font>

282
00:17:14,188 --> 00:17:16,464
<font color=#FFFF00>We've already suffered
enough because of you.</font>

283
00:17:16,488 --> 00:17:18,988
<font color=#FFFF00>- Well...
- What's going on here?</font>

284
00:17:19,888 --> 00:17:21,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Good morning, Director Bang.</font>

285
00:17:22,048 --> 00:17:23,648
<font color=#FFFF00>What brings you here, Dong Hui?</font>

286
00:17:24,918 --> 00:17:27,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Who is she?</font>

287
00:17:27,358 --> 00:17:29,394
<font color=#FFFF00>Let me introduce her to you.</font>

288
00:17:29,418 --> 00:17:31,088
<font color=#FFFF00>You know Writer Choi Jin Kyung, right?</font>

289
00:17:31,488 --> 00:17:32,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Pardon?</font>

290
00:17:33,218 --> 00:17:35,287
<font color=#FFFF00>She wrote a miniseries called,</font>

291
00:17:35,288 --> 00:17:37,688
<font color=#FFFF00>"Icarus's Wings: the Golden Times".</font>

292
00:17:37,988 --> 00:17:39,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello. I'm Choi Jin Kyung.</font>

293
00:17:41,218 --> 00:17:44,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Where is Director Han? We have
to sign a contract today.</font>

294
00:17:46,788 --> 00:17:50,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Han. Please say hello.
This is Writer Choi Jin Kyung.</font>

295
00:17:50,858 --> 00:17:54,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello, Director Han. I've
heard a lot about you.</font>

296
00:18:05,618 --> 00:18:06,948
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry,</font>

297
00:18:07,288 --> 00:18:09,608
<font color=#FFFF00>but I was aware that I was to
write the scripts on my own.</font>

298
00:18:10,418 --> 00:18:13,418
<font color=#FFFF00>It's about the same as writing
the scripts on your own.</font>

299
00:18:13,618 --> 00:18:15,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Oh Dong Hui wrote the synopsis.</font>

300
00:18:15,858 --> 00:18:18,217
<font color=#FFFF00>We scouted you for a writer...</font>

301
00:18:18,218 --> 00:18:20,147
<font color=#FFFF00>who will write even better scripts.</font>

302
00:18:20,148 --> 00:18:21,748
<font color=#FFFF00>I hope you wouldn't be offended.</font>

303
00:18:21,948 --> 00:18:24,918
<font color=#FFFF00>I never agreed to sell my synopsis.</font>

304
00:18:25,018 --> 00:18:28,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you telling me that you will
write the scripts all on your own?</font>

305
00:18:28,948 --> 00:18:30,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Bang.</font>

306
00:18:30,188 --> 00:18:31,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Then, what is your plan?</font>

307
00:18:32,488 --> 00:18:35,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Writer Choi, please help us.</font>

308
00:18:35,318 --> 00:18:37,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Producer Park insists on
directing this drama.</font>

309
00:18:38,088 --> 00:18:40,918
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't depend on Ms. Oh Dong Hui
since she's an inexperienced writer.</font>

310
00:18:41,618 --> 00:18:43,918
<font color=#FFFF00>We have no other way around it.</font>

311
00:18:44,188 --> 00:18:46,917
<font color=#FFFF00>So do you mean that I have to co-write...</font>

312
00:18:46,918 --> 00:18:48,688
<font color=#FFFF00>with a rookie like her?</font>

313
00:18:48,948 --> 00:18:52,418
<font color=#FFFF00>I also do not wish to co-write
my drama with another writer.</font>

314
00:18:52,688 --> 00:18:53,788
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

315
00:18:54,088 --> 00:18:56,858
<font color=#FFFF00>How old are you? How many
dramas have you written?</font>

316
00:18:57,318 --> 00:18:59,857
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Bang. How can you
handle business like this?</font>

317
00:18:59,858 --> 00:19:01,618
<font color=#FFFF00>This is also an insult to Writer Choi, too.</font>

318
00:19:02,018 --> 00:19:04,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Fine. Then, I will make a
suggestion to both of you.</font>

319
00:19:06,948 --> 00:19:09,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Writer Choi, if you help us out this time,</font>

320
00:19:09,748 --> 00:19:12,288
<font color=#FFFF00>we will sign you for the next drama.</font>

321
00:19:13,858 --> 00:19:15,018
<font color=#FFFF00>And for you, Ms. Oh Dong Hui.</font>

322
00:19:15,518 --> 00:19:17,718
<font color=#FFFF00>Since you won't sell your synopsis,</font>

323
00:19:17,818 --> 00:19:20,148
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll treat you like a writer, then.</font>

324
00:19:20,918 --> 00:19:24,548
<font color=#FFFF00>However, it will only air after you
have proved yourself as a writer.</font>

325
00:19:25,418 --> 00:19:26,518
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

326
00:19:27,088 --> 00:19:29,748
<font color=#FFFF00>We will go ahead with her synopsis,</font>

327
00:19:30,148 --> 00:19:32,688
<font color=#FFFF00>but both of you will write the
scripts based on the synopsis.</font>

328
00:19:32,858 --> 00:19:36,294
<font color=#FFFF00>We will go with the scripts
that seem to be written better.</font>

329
00:19:36,318 --> 00:19:37,358
<font color=#FFFF00>How can that be possible?</font>

330
00:19:37,588 --> 00:19:39,287
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Bang. Is this how you handle...</font>

331
00:19:39,288 --> 00:19:41,588
<font color=#FFFF00>I am aware that I may be
asking a bit much from you.</font>

332
00:19:42,088 --> 00:19:45,217
<font color=#FFFF00>However, don't worry since a
rookie writer like her...</font>

333
00:19:45,218 --> 00:19:46,648
<font color=#FFFF00>can't defeat you.</font>

334
00:19:48,518 --> 00:19:50,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Now the decision remains
solely on your hands.</font>

335
00:19:52,288 --> 00:19:53,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Ms. Oh Dong Hui.</font>

336
00:19:53,858 --> 00:19:56,417
<font color=#FFFF00>This is a good way for you to
squash any rumor that claims...</font>

337
00:19:56,418 --> 00:19:59,618
<font color=#FFFF00>you became a writer by someone's
help, not by your own merit.</font>

338
00:20:06,618 --> 00:20:09,218
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you think? Are you not confident?</font>

339
00:20:11,118 --> 00:20:12,948
<font color=#FFFF00>If you are not, then stay out of it.</font>

340
00:20:23,358 --> 00:20:26,718
<font color=#FFFF00>Why did you willingly
accept her suggestion?</font>

341
00:20:27,388 --> 00:20:28,864
<font color=#FFFF00>If not?</font>

342
00:20:28,888 --> 00:20:31,418
<font color=#FFFF00>She might think I'm running
away because I'm scared.</font>

343
00:20:31,618 --> 00:20:33,518
<font color=#FFFF00>You should have protected your synopsis.</font>

344
00:20:33,618 --> 00:20:37,394
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you compete with another
writer with a synopsis you wrote?</font>

345
00:20:37,418 --> 00:20:40,018
<font color=#FFFF00>If I don't, she won't
acknowledge me as a writer.</font>

346
00:20:40,188 --> 00:20:42,294
<font color=#FFFF00>If I say I will write
the scripts on my own,</font>

347
00:20:42,318 --> 00:20:44,648
<font color=#FFFF00>do you think she would approve?</font>

348
00:20:45,388 --> 00:20:46,518
<font color=#FFFF00>You're right, but...</font>

349
00:20:47,418 --> 00:20:49,088
<font color=#FFFF00>This is just too sad.</font>

350
00:20:49,358 --> 00:20:51,078
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't do anything about it even if it is.</font>

351
00:20:51,248 --> 00:20:52,858
<font color=#FFFF00>All I can do is win.</font>

352
00:20:52,988 --> 00:20:54,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

353
00:20:54,248 --> 00:20:57,548
<font color=#FFFF00>Please leave now. I'm going
to start right away.</font>

354
00:21:25,788 --> 00:21:28,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think this is some
sort of a game or a trick?</font>

355
00:21:28,788 --> 00:21:30,288
<font color=#FFFF00>How can two writers
compete with each other?</font>

356
00:21:30,388 --> 00:21:32,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Why? Did I hurt your feelings?</font>

357
00:21:32,618 --> 00:21:35,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Drama is like a living creature.</font>

358
00:21:35,418 --> 00:21:37,194
<font color=#FFFF00>It's hard enough for one writer
to come up with the scripts.</font>

359
00:21:37,218 --> 00:21:39,148
<font color=#FFFF00>How can they alternate episodes and write?</font>

360
00:21:39,648 --> 00:21:41,568
<font color=#FFFF00>Who said they will alternate
episodes and write?</font>

361
00:21:42,318 --> 00:21:43,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. You are confident.</font>

362
00:21:44,888 --> 00:21:45,948
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

363
00:21:46,118 --> 00:21:48,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Writer Choi has an experience
of 10 years in scriptwriting.</font>

364
00:21:48,918 --> 00:21:51,217
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think Dong Hui can
write better than...</font>

365
00:21:51,218 --> 00:21:53,718
<font color=#FFFF00>Writer Choi even if it's just one episode?</font>

366
00:21:54,188 --> 00:21:55,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Bang Mi Joo!</font>

367
00:21:55,548 --> 00:21:57,794
<font color=#FFFF00>Whether Writer Choi wins or she does,</font>

368
00:21:57,818 --> 00:22:00,518
<font color=#FFFF00>it won't hurt our team in any
way since we will be airing...</font>

369
00:22:00,788 --> 00:22:03,418
<font color=#FFFF00>the episodes of better written scripts.</font>

370
00:22:03,688 --> 00:22:04,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Isn't that enough?</font>

371
00:22:06,818 --> 00:22:08,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't worry too much.</font>

372
00:22:08,248 --> 00:22:10,888
<font color=#FFFF00>You said she is a good writer.</font>

373
00:22:11,088 --> 00:22:12,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Then, she will win.</font>

374
00:22:13,918 --> 00:22:16,964
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway, you usually turn off
your phone when you go home.</font>

375
00:22:16,988 --> 00:22:19,518
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm grateful that you're calling me now.</font>

376
00:22:20,948 --> 00:22:23,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Well, then. Good night. Bye now.</font>

377
00:22:43,288 --> 00:22:45,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Moong Chi, be quiet. Don't
you know I'm writing now?</font>

378
00:22:47,288 --> 00:22:50,418
<font color=#FFFF00>This is very important to me.
I have to win.</font>

379
00:22:50,618 --> 00:22:51,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Be quiet!</font>

380
00:23:02,348 --> 00:23:03,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you going somewhere?</font>

381
00:23:03,718 --> 00:23:06,548
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. I have to meet someone.</font>

382
00:23:06,818 --> 00:23:08,338
<font color=#FFFF00>Who are you meeting at this late hour?</font>

383
00:23:09,018 --> 00:23:10,618
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm meeting a coworker.</font>

384
00:23:11,418 --> 00:23:12,487
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll be back.</font>

385
00:23:12,488 --> 00:23:13,747
<font color=#FFFF00>Come home early.</font>

386
00:23:13,748 --> 00:23:14,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay.</font>

387
00:23:20,918 --> 00:23:21,948
<font color=#FFFF00>How's Father?</font>

388
00:23:22,318 --> 00:23:24,188
<font color=#FFFF00>I saw him at home before I left.</font>

389
00:23:24,918 --> 00:23:27,118
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on?</font>

390
00:23:27,588 --> 00:23:30,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Why do I have to keep
this a secret from him?</font>

391
00:23:34,788 --> 00:23:35,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon.</font>

392
00:23:37,618 --> 00:23:39,648
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry to bring this to you.</font>

393
00:23:41,248 --> 00:23:43,488
<font color=#FFFF00>I think Father is in trouble.</font>

394
00:23:44,218 --> 00:23:45,288
<font color=#FFFF00>What kind of trouble?</font>

395
00:23:46,088 --> 00:23:48,118
<font color=#FFFF00>He won't tell me what it is.</font>

396
00:23:49,318 --> 00:23:52,318
<font color=#FFFF00>You know the woman with Father you
saw on the street the other day?</font>

397
00:23:54,888 --> 00:23:57,947
<font color=#FFFF00>Let go of me. I can't help you anymore.</font>

398
00:23:57,948 --> 00:23:59,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Go. Leave now.</font>

399
00:23:59,848 --> 00:24:01,248
<font color=#FFFF00>You must be Seong Joon.</font>

400
00:24:01,818 --> 00:24:03,318
