<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think I'm a woman who would wait...</font>

598
00:36:27,348 --> 00:36:29,148
<font color=#FFFF00>for a guy to return for 30 years?</font>

599
00:36:30,218 --> 00:36:32,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't be ridiculous.</font>

600
00:36:32,918 --> 00:36:34,048
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sorry.</font>

601
00:36:34,488 --> 00:36:37,518
<font color=#FFFF00>No. You don't need to be.
Why are you sorry?</font>

602
00:36:37,648 --> 00:36:40,818
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not like you hurt me,</font>

603
00:36:41,018 --> 00:36:44,588
<font color=#FFFF00>made me waste my time, or humiliated me.</font>

604
00:36:44,888 --> 00:36:47,258
<font color=#FFFF00>I've been just fine. I've been happy.</font>

605
00:36:48,788 --> 00:36:49,948
<font color=#FFFF00>My point is...</font>

606
00:36:50,888 --> 00:36:52,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you ever...</font>

607
00:36:53,418 --> 00:36:55,218
<font color=#FFFF00>show your face again from now on.</font>

608
00:36:56,048 --> 00:36:57,988
<font color=#FFFF00>- Ae Ri.
- If you really...</font>

609
00:36:59,288 --> 00:37:01,688
<font color=#FFFF00>loved me by any chance,</font>

610
00:37:02,218 --> 00:37:04,988
<font color=#FFFF00>please do this for me.</font>

611
00:37:07,588 --> 00:37:09,548
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't want to see you ever again.</font>

612
00:37:11,218 --> 00:37:14,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Ae Ri. Ae Ri.</font>

613
00:37:14,618 --> 00:37:15,758
<font color=#FFFF00>Ae Ri.</font>

614
00:37:20,918 --> 00:37:23,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Ae Ri. Ae Ri!</font>

615
00:39:05,518 --> 00:39:06,618
<font color=#FFFF00>Welcome, Director Han.</font>

616
00:39:12,788 --> 00:39:13,848
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello.</font>

617
00:39:15,788 --> 00:39:18,258
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello. We meet again.</font>

618
00:39:18,588 --> 00:39:21,148
<font color=#FFFF00>He came to check the contract himself.</font>

619
00:39:24,218 --> 00:39:26,048
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing? Take a seat.</font>

620
00:39:32,648 --> 00:39:34,394
<font color=#FFFF00>I wanted to check the office atmosphere...</font>

621
00:39:34,418 --> 00:39:36,988
<font color=#FFFF00>as well as get some things done.</font>

622
00:39:38,918 --> 00:39:41,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Is everything going as
planned, Director Han?</font>

623
00:39:41,818 --> 00:39:45,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes. Thanks to you, the
production is running smoothly.</font>

624
00:39:46,388 --> 00:39:49,088
<font color=#FFFF00>We will sign a contract with a writer soon.</font>

625
00:39:50,048 --> 00:39:51,048
<font color=#FFFF00>I see.</font>

626
00:39:52,318 --> 00:39:54,464
<font color=#FFFF00>I have no doubt...</font>

627
00:39:54,488 --> 00:39:56,218
<font color=#FFFF00>that you will handle things well.</font>

628
00:39:57,048 --> 00:39:58,788
<font color=#FFFF00>If this investment turns out as a success,</font>

629
00:39:59,118 --> 00:40:01,624
<font color=#FFFF00>I plan to expand the investment...</font>

630
00:40:01,648 --> 00:40:03,148
<font color=#FFFF00>in Korean drama production.</font>

631
00:40:03,388 --> 00:40:05,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Is that right?</font>

632
00:40:05,318 --> 00:40:09,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course, I'd appreciate it
if Director Han is involved.</font>

633
00:40:09,818 --> 00:40:11,688
<font color=#FFFF00>This investment will be a success.</font>

634
00:40:12,088 --> 00:40:14,948
<font color=#FFFF00>And the next project will
be influenced by it.</font>

635
00:40:15,918 --> 00:40:17,418
<font color=#FFFF00>You've made a right choice.</font>

636
00:40:19,348 --> 00:40:21,618
<font color=#FFFF00>I think so, too.</font>

637
00:40:30,148 --> 00:40:31,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Mr. Lee.</font>

638
00:40:37,348 --> 00:40:38,418
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on?</font>

639
00:40:38,688 --> 00:40:39,818
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

640
00:40:40,718 --> 00:40:42,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't you know why I came here?</font>

641
00:40:42,718 --> 00:40:44,088
<font color=#FFFF00>No, not that.</font>

642
00:40:45,418 --> 00:40:48,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Can I ask you why you decided to come back?</font>

643
00:40:51,588 --> 00:40:53,148
<font color=#FFFF00>I realized...</font>

644
00:40:53,588 --> 00:40:56,418
<font color=#FFFF00>that I had unfinished businesses.</font>

645
00:40:56,918 --> 00:40:58,218
<font color=#FFFF00>That's why I came back.</font>

646
00:40:59,758 --> 00:41:02,918
<font color=#FFFF00>But I don't plan to stay too long.</font>

647
00:41:05,218 --> 00:41:06,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Anyway,</font>

648
00:41:07,048 --> 00:41:08,448
<font color=#FFFF00>I wish you good luck, Director Han.</font>

649
00:41:55,388 --> 00:41:56,848
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing here?</font>

650
00:42:01,118 --> 00:42:02,118
<font color=#FFFF00>You're home.</font>

651
00:42:04,388 --> 00:42:05,688
<font color=#FFFF00>How did you get in here?</font>

652
00:42:07,988 --> 00:42:09,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you forget?</font>

653
00:42:09,618 --> 00:42:13,288
<font color=#FFFF00>We used to be a couple. I
know your gate password.</font>

654
00:42:13,848 --> 00:42:15,948
<font color=#FFFF00>I heard you came back, so I stopped by.</font>

655
00:42:23,648 --> 00:42:25,618
<font color=#FFFF00>Get out. Get out now.</font>

656
00:42:28,948 --> 00:42:31,418
<font color=#FFFF00>You should've cleaned the house
as soon as you came back.</font>

657
00:42:31,788 --> 00:42:33,717
<font color=#FFFF00>Even if you are only
staying for a short while,</font>

658
00:42:33,718 --> 00:42:36,648
<font color=#FFFF00>you should make the house liveable.</font>

659
00:42:37,048 --> 00:42:40,618
<font color=#FFFF00>I got groceries in a hurry, so I
couldn't get too many things.</font>

660
00:42:40,818 --> 00:42:42,918
<font color=#FFFF00>I will make a few side dishes first.</font>

661
00:42:55,618 --> 00:42:57,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Please go now. Please.</font>

662
00:42:59,648 --> 00:43:00,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Then...</font>

663
00:43:01,258 --> 00:43:03,018
<font color=#FFFF00>help me understand the situation.</font>

664
00:43:03,488 --> 00:43:05,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Or else, I will never be able
to accept this situation.</font>

665
00:43:05,888 --> 00:43:07,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell me why you suddenly came back.</font>

666
00:43:08,048 --> 00:43:10,758
<font color=#FFFF00>It's understandable that
you suddenly came back.</font>

667
00:43:11,258 --> 00:43:13,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Just tell me why you've changed.</font>

668
00:43:14,818 --> 00:43:15,848
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeong Eun.</font>

669
00:43:16,788 --> 00:43:17,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you stupid?</font>

670
00:43:18,258 --> 00:43:19,518
<font color=#FFFF00>We broke up.</font>

671
00:43:19,848 --> 00:43:21,818
<font color=#FFFF00>But you came back.</font>

672
00:43:21,918 --> 00:43:23,648
<font color=#FFFF00>What difference does it make?</font>

673
00:43:26,148 --> 00:43:27,218
<font color=#FFFF00>What did you say?</font>

674
00:43:27,318 --> 00:43:29,678
<font color=#FFFF00>Does that make any difference
to the fact that we split up?</font>

675
00:43:30,758 --> 00:43:32,588
<font color=#FFFF00>It's okay for a man and
a woman to split up.</font>

676
00:43:33,288 --> 00:43:36,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you being all clingy because
of your lingering feelings?</font>

677
00:43:38,218 --> 00:43:39,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you say clingy?</font>

678
00:43:40,118 --> 00:43:41,358
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you say lingering feelings?</font>

679
00:43:42,248 --> 00:43:43,388
<font color=#FFFF00>What happened?</font>

680
00:43:44,048 --> 00:43:46,648
<font color=#FFFF00>What happened to you?</font>

681
00:43:48,718 --> 00:43:50,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you doing this to me?</font>

682
00:43:53,948 --> 00:43:55,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Please leave...</font>

683
00:43:55,788 --> 00:43:56,948
<font color=#FFFF00>when I ask nicely.</font>

684
00:43:58,188 --> 00:44:00,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't do this. You don't
have to be this mean.</font>

685
00:44:00,948 --> 00:44:02,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Without you,</font>

686
00:44:02,318 --> 00:44:05,318
<font color=#FFFF00>a week felt like a year.</font>

687
00:44:05,418 --> 00:44:07,987
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't know what happened
to you over the week,</font>

688
00:44:07,988 --> 00:44:10,248
<font color=#FFFF00>but you don't have to be like this to me.</font>

689
00:44:11,788 --> 00:44:13,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Nothing happened.</font>

690
00:44:14,018 --> 00:44:15,148
<font color=#FFFF00>I just...</font>

691
00:44:16,148 --> 00:44:17,648
<font color=#FFFF00>don't have...</font>

692
00:44:18,418 --> 00:44:20,048
<font color=#FFFF00>a place for you in my heart.</font>

693
00:44:22,488 --> 00:44:23,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Hyun Woo.</font>

694
00:44:24,518 --> 00:44:25,748
<font color=#FFFF00>So please leave.</font>

695
00:44:27,618 --> 00:44:29,048
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't want to talk more.</font>

696
00:44:32,518 --> 00:44:34,288
<font color=#FFFF00>How can you do this to me?</font>

697
00:44:35,218 --> 00:44:36,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Then...</font>

698
00:44:36,988 --> 00:44:39,148
<font color=#FFFF00>what were you doing with me all along?</font>

699
00:44:40,248 --> 00:44:41,548
<font color=#FFFF00>Were you playing with me?</font>

700
00:44:43,288 --> 00:44:44,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

701
00:44:45,018 --> 00:44:46,218
<font color=#FFFF00>I was playing with you.</font>

702
00:44:48,888 --> 00:44:49,918
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

703
00:44:50,288 --> 00:44:51,988
<font color=#FFFF00>I had a little fun with you.</font>

704
00:44:52,748 --> 00:44:53,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you get it now?</font>

705
00:45:35,248 --> 00:45:36,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are you going at this hour?</font>

706
00:45:37,018 --> 00:45:39,588
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm going up to the studio.</font>

707
00:45:39,788 --> 00:45:40,888
<font color=#FFFF00>The studio?</font>

708
00:45:41,388 --> 00:45:43,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you mean Dong Hui's studio?
Why are you going at this hour?</font>

709
00:45:44,248 --> 00:45:45,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom.</font>

710
00:45:45,618 --> 00:45:47,524
<font color=#FFFF00>How many times did I tell you?</font>

711
00:45:47,548 --> 00:45:50,747
<font color=#FFFF00>We are family, but you shouldn't
go up to Dong Hui's room so often.</font>

712
00:45:50,748 --> 00:45:52,648
<font color=#FFFF00>- People will talk about it.
- Mom.</font>

713
00:45:52,818 --> 00:45:54,517
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui's my staff.</font>

714
00:45:54,518 --> 00:45:56,517
<font color=#FFFF00>And she will be writing the
new drama we're producing.</font>

715
00:45:56,518 --> 00:45:58,638
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop it. I don't know those things.
Just don't go up.</font>

716
00:45:58,818 --> 00:46:00,548
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong with you?</font>

717
00:46:12,618 --> 00:46:13,648
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

718
00:46:14,988 --> 00:46:16,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you asleep?</font>

719
00:46:16,618 --> 00:46:17,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Aren't you going to write?</font>

720
00:46:21,218 --> 00:46:22,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui?</font>

721
00:46:24,248 --> 00:46:25,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

722
00:46:31,348 --> 00:46:32,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui.</font>

723
00:46:38,288 --> 00:46:39,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui, what's wrong?</font>

724
00:46:39,848 --> 00:46:42,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you sick? Is something wrong?</font>

725
00:46:45,148 --> 00:46:46,618
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong?</font>

726
00:46:48,418 --> 00:46:49,818
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui!</font>

727
00:46:55,188 --> 00:46:56,518
<font color=#FFFF00>What's wrong? What is it?</font>

728
00:46:58,818 --> 00:47:00,418
<font color=#FFFF00>I am scared.</font>

729
00:47:02,388 --> 00:47:04,487
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't think I can do this.</font>

730
00:47:04,488 --> 00:47:07,024
<font color=#FFFF00>No matter how much I think about
it, I don't think I can do it.</font>

731
00:47:07,048 --> 00:47:09,487
<font color=#FFFF00>I think it's better...</font>

732
00:47:09,488 --> 00:47:11,888
<font color=#FFFF00>to ask Writer Choi to write everything.</font>

733
00:47:12,018 --> 00:47:15,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Tell her she can write the
script using my synopsis.</font>

734
00:47:17,618 --> 00:47:18,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Give me the blanket.</font>

735
00:47:19,188 --> 00:47:21,748
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm scared, and I need to put it over me.</font>

736
00:47:21,988 --> 00:47:24,418
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm embarrassed, too.</font>

737
00:47:26,648 --> 00:47:27,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui!</font>

738
00:47:29,548 --> 00:47:33,348
<font color=#FFFF00>She's a veteran writer with
10 years of experience,</font>

739
00:47:33,488 --> 00:47:36,718
<font color=#FFFF00>while I'm literally a novice writer.</font>

740
00:47:37,318 --> 00:47:41,588
<font color=#FFFF00>How on earth do you think I can beat her?</font>

741
00:47:42,018 --> 00:47:45,618
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm no match for her in the first place.</font>

742
00:47:46,288 --> 00:47:48,418
<font color=#FFFF00>You are very silly, Dong Hui.</font>

743
00:47:51,088 --> 00:47:54,088
<font color=#FFFF00>You're right. I am silly.</font>

744
00:47:55,548 --> 00:47:57,748
<font color=#FFFF00>I know I was too reckless.</font>

745
00:47:58,488 --> 00:48:01,288
<font color=#FFFF00>So please leave me alone.</font>

746
00:48:18,388 --> 00:48:20,748
<font color=#FFFF00>- Follow me.
- Sorry?</font>

747
00:48:26,048 --> 00:48:28,418
<font color=#FFFF00>- Where are we going?
- Get up now.</font>

748
00:48:53,788 --> 00:48:56,088
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you doing now?</font>

749
00:48:56,688 --> 00:48:58,688
<font color=#FFFF00>- Just buckle up.
- Pardon?</font>

750
00:49:08,488 --> 00:49:10,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Please tell me where we are going.</font>

751
00:49:10,988 --> 00:49:13,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Why? Are you afraid that I
might sell you to someone?</font>

752
00:49:14,118 --> 00:49:16,318
<font color=#FFFF00>I won't be able to sell you
at a high price, anyway.</font>

753
00:49:17,118 --> 00:49:20,048
<font color=#FFFF00>No one would buy a novice
writer who cries out of fear.</font>

754
00:49:20,418 --> 00:49:21,418
<font color=#FFFF00>What did you say?</font>

755
00:49:23,018 --> 00:49:25,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Just tell me where we are heading.</font>

756
00:49:25,218 --> 00:49:28,088
<font color=#FFFF00>- You'll see soon.
- I have no time for this.</font>

757
00:49:28,248 --> 00:49:30,588
<font color=#FFFF00>I have to hand in my
script by this Wednesday.</font>

758
00:49:31,188 --> 00:49:34,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Didn't you say you gave up and
you'll leave it to Writer Choi?</font>

759
00:49:34,948 --> 00:49:36,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Be quiet and have some sleep.</font>

760
00:49:52,248 --> 00:49:54,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui, we're here. Wake up.</font>

761
00:49:56,618 --> 00:49:57,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are we?</font>

762
00:50:00,188 --> 00:50:01,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Just get off.</font>

763
00:50:26,188 --> 00:50:27,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Isn't this amazing?</font>

764
00:50:28,018 --> 00:50:30,418
<font color=#FFFF00>I didn't know there's
such a place in Korea.</font>

765
00:50:31,818 --> 00:50:33,548
<font color=#FFFF00>I love this smell of books.</font>

766
00:50:35,218 --> 00:50:38,118
<font color=#FFFF00>- These aren't mere books.
- Sorry?</font>

767
00:50:39,148 --> 00:50:42,318
<font color=#FFFF00>These are the fruits of the
writers who have overcome...</font>

768
00:50:42,588 --> 00:50:43,948
<font color=#FFFF00>dreadful fear of creation.</font>

769
00:50:55,588 --> 00:50:56,668
<font color=#FFFF00>This is Ernest Hemingway's.</font>

770
00:50:58,418 --> 00:51:01,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Hemingway once said this.</font>

771
00:51:01,988 --> 00:51:04,888
<font color=#FFFF00>"There is nothing to writing."</font>

772
00:51:05,788 --> 00:51:07,488
<font color=#FFFF00>"All you do is..."</font>

773
00:51:07,648 --> 00:51:10,518
<font color=#FFFF00>"sit down at a typewriter and bleed."</font>

774
00:51:11,688 --> 00:51:13,948
<font color=#FFFF00>He rewrote the last part...</font>

775
00:51:14,288 --> 00:51:17,648
<font color=#FFFF00>of "A Farewell to Arms" 39 times.</font>

776
00:51:45,318 --> 00:51:46,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you like Haruki Murakami?</font>

777
00:51:51,188 --> 00:51:52,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Murakami...</font>

778
00:51:53,288 --> 00:51:56,918
<font color=#FFFF00>gets up at three in the
morning and writes...</font>

779
00:51:57,348 --> 00:51:59,518
<font color=#FFFF00>until noon every day.</font>

780
00:52:00,388 --> 00:52:04,548
<font color=#FFFF00>In the afternoon, he runs...</font>

781
00:52:04,818 --> 00:52:07,118
<font color=#FFFF00>to maintain his good condition for writing.</font>

782
00:52:10,018 --> 00:52:13,188
<font color=#FFFF00>How does it feel like to find
out other writers' efforts?</font>

783
00:52:17,488 --> 00:52:19,488
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm sure no writers wrote their works...</font>

784
00:52:20,388 --> 00:52:22,888
<font color=#FFFF00>very easily without any
pain or hardworking.</font>

785
00:52:25,118 --> 00:52:28,788
<font color=#FFFF00>All the great writers have gone
through the torment of creativity.</font>

786
00:52:29,518 --> 00:52:31,358
<font color=#FFFF00>How would you think you'd
be able to avoid it?</font>

787
00:52:31,918 --> 00:52:34,848
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you think you could write it overnight?</font>

788
00:52:36,218 --> 00:52:37,948
<font color=#FFFF00>I never said that.</font>

789
00:52:39,288 --> 00:52:42,888
<font color=#FFFF00>I am afraid. I'm scared to death.</font>

790
00:52:43,218 --> 00:52:45,348
<font color=#FFFF00>What about the writers of all these books?</font>

791
00:52:45,648 --> 00:52:47,188
<font color=#FFFF00>They have felt the same.</font>

792
00:52:48,418 --> 00:52:52,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Everyone is afraid of unknown paths.</font>

793
00:52:52,518 --> 00:52:55,848
<font color=#FFFF00>But if you give up and stop moving forward,</font>

794
00:52:56,188 --> 00:52:58,588
<font color=#FFFF00>you'll never be able to find
out the beautiful things...</font>

795
00:52:58,748 --> 00:53:00,308
<font color=#FFFF00>waiting for you at the end of the path.</font>

796
00:53:00,888 --> 00:53:02,688
<font color=#FFFF00>All you need to do...</font>

797
00:53:03,248 --> 00:53:04,918
<font color=#FFFF00>is take the first step.</font>

798
00:53:05,348 --> 00:53:07,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you say you're scared? Everyone is.</font>

799
00:53:08,388 --> 00:53:09,948
<font color=#FFFF00>You just have to overcome it.</font>

800
00:53:12,918 --> 00:53:16,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Will I be able to do it?</font>

801
00:53:17,248 --> 00:53:19,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course, you will.</font>

802
00:53:20,548 --> 00:53:22,148
<font color=#FFFF00>What if I fail?</font>

803
00:53:25,218 --> 00:53:26,788
<font color=#FFFF00>You just made...</font>

804
00:53:27,848 --> 00:53:29,518
<font color=#FFFF00>what I've said so far meaningless.</font>

805
00:53:29,818 --> 00:53:31,717
<font color=#FFFF00>I'm seriously afraid.</font>

806
00:53:31,718 --> 00:53:34,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Then, give up everything and marry me.</font>

807
00:53:35,318 --> 00:53:36,548
<font color=#FFFF00>Pardon?</font>

808
00:53:38,418 --> 00:53:41,348
<font color=#FFFF00>What on earth are you talking about?</font>

809
00:53:42,148 --> 00:53:44,918
<font color=#FFFF00>I was going to listen to you as
you said a lot of great things.</font>

810
00:53:45,288 --> 00:53:48,248
<font color=#FFFF00>- And what's this?
- Then, just keep writing.</font>

811
00:53:48,418 --> 00:53:50,618
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop whining like a baby.</font>

812
00:53:51,048 --> 00:53:55,118
<font color=#FFFF00>You should know so many writers
desperately want to write like you.</font>

813
00:53:55,218 --> 00:53:57,064
<font color=#FFFF00>Why are you yelling at me?</font>

814
00:53:57,088 --> 00:53:59,588
<font color=#FFFF00>I do know how to yell just like you.</font>

815
00:54:00,888 --> 00:54:03,848
<font color=#FFFF00>This is ridiculous. You're something else!</font>

816
00:54:04,088 --> 00:54:05,617
<font color=#FFFF00>This is great.</font>

817
00:54:05,618 --> 00:54:08,918
<font color=#FFFF00>I was stressed out anyway.
Let's get nasty, then.</font>

818
00:54:09,348 --> 00:54:13,318
<font color=#FFFF00>You won't be able to write a line.
Stop nagging at me.</font>

819
00:54:14,088 --> 00:54:17,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Why don't you go start writing
and see if it works as you want?</font>

820
00:54:17,848 --> 00:54:20,488
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you think I'd be here shouting
like this if it was that easy?</font>

821
00:54:31,048 --> 00:54:32,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Please...</font>

822
00:54:33,248 --> 00:54:34,588
<font color=#FFFF00>take it easy and keep writing.</font>

823
00:54:35,318 --> 00:54:37,418
<font color=#FFFF00>I know you can do it. I got your back.</font>

824
00:54:39,118 --> 00:54:42,418
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll be by your side so
that you won't feel afraid.</font>

825
00:54:43,218 --> 00:54:44,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Okay?</font>

826
00:55:36,218 --> 00:55:37,418
<font color=#FFFF00>What was that?</font>

827
00:55:37,588 --> 00:55:40,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Stop making excuses and keep writing, okay?</font>

828
00:55:47,118 --> 00:55:49,718
<font color=#FFFF00>Come with me. I'll show
you my favorite book.</font>

829
00:55:55,188 --> 00:55:57,248
<font color=#FFFF00>"I sat and watched her
sleep, a little troubled,"</font>

830
00:55:58,218 --> 00:56:00,318
<font color=#FFFF00>"deep down in my soul,"</font>

831
00:56:00,888 --> 00:56:03,918
<font color=#FFFF00>"but kept holy by the clear night
which has never given me..."</font>

832
00:56:04,648 --> 00:56:06,048
<font color=#FFFF00>"other than beautiful thoughts"</font>

833
00:56:10,888 --> 00:56:13,048
<font color=#FFFF00>"Around us the stars continued..."</font>

834
00:56:13,688 --> 00:56:16,088
<font color=#FFFF00>"heir silent march,"</font>

835
00:56:16,488 --> 00:56:18,048
<font color=#FFFF00>"obedient as a mighty army."</font>

836
00:56:19,948 --> 00:56:21,388
<font color=#FFFF00>"I fancied that one of these stars,"</font>

837
00:56:22,148 --> 00:56:25,018
<font color=#FFFF00>"the most delicate, the most lustrous,"</font>

838
00:56:25,418 --> 00:56:27,348
<font color=#FFFF00>"had missed her way..."</font>

839
00:56:28,388 --> 00:56:29,388
<font color=#FFFF00>"and had come..."</font>

840
00:56:29,948 --> 00:56:32,348
<font color=#FFFF00>"to lean upon my shoulder, and to sleep."</font>

841
00:56:43,688 --> 00:56:45,248
<font color=#FFFF00>("The Stars" by Alphonse Daudet)</font>

842
00:57:15,318 --> 00:57:16,758
<font color=#FFFF00>(FGC personnel records, Oh Dong Hui)</font>

843
00:57:20,888 --> 00:57:24,148
<font color=#FFFF00>(Agreement for writing scenario
and transfer of the copyright)</font>

844
00:57:40,418 --> 00:57:41,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Hello?</font>

845
00:57:42,188 --> 00:57:43,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Mom, it's me.</font>

846
00:57:50,218 --> 00:57:51,948
<font color=#FFFF00>It's me, Gwang Jin.</font>

847
00:57:52,788 --> 00:57:56,348
<font color=#FFFF00>You sound so surprised, and
I feel bad for calling now.</font>

848
00:57:56,648 --> 00:57:59,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Right. How are you doing?</font>

849
00:57:59,788 --> 00:58:01,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Have you finished the herbal medicine?</font>

850
00:58:02,518 --> 00:58:03,948
<font color=#FFFF00>I still have some.</font>

851
00:58:04,318 --> 00:58:07,048
<font color=#FFFF00>You shouldn't trouble yourself
with those things now.</font>

852
00:58:07,148 --> 00:58:09,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't say that.</font>

853
00:58:11,118 --> 00:58:12,488
<font color=#FFFF00>By the way,</font>

854
00:58:14,148 --> 00:58:17,748
<font color=#FFFF00>I am looking at your
granddaughter Dong Hui's resume.</font>

855
00:58:19,788 --> 00:58:20,788
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

856
00:58:22,088 --> 00:58:23,218
<font color=#FFFF00>But...</font>

857
00:58:23,788 --> 00:58:25,788
<font color=#FFFF00>she doesn't look anything like you</font>

858
00:58:28,748 --> 00:58:31,518
<font color=#FFFF00>She looks like her father.</font>

859
00:58:31,888 --> 00:58:34,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you call to say that?</font>

860
00:58:34,348 --> 00:58:37,848
<font color=#FFFF00>Of course not. I wanted to tell you
that you've brought her up well.</font>

861
00:58:38,148 --> 00:58:39,818
<font color=#FFFF00>I see that she's a writer.</font>

862
00:58:41,248 --> 00:58:42,748
<font color=#FFFF00>What do you mean?</font>

863
00:58:44,518 --> 00:58:47,188
<font color=#FFFF00>She started out as an
assistant at our office,</font>

864
00:58:48,418 --> 00:58:51,018
<font color=#FFFF00>and now we are signing a
contract with her as a writer.</font>

865
00:58:52,718 --> 00:58:53,888
<font color=#FFFF00>How did it...</font>

866
00:58:55,348 --> 00:58:58,618
<font color=#FFFF00>Director Bang brought it
to me for a final confirm,</font>

867
00:58:59,088 --> 00:59:00,718
<font color=#FFFF00>and it turned out...</font>

868
00:59:01,048 --> 00:59:02,748
<font color=#FFFF00>it was your granddaughter.</font>

869
00:59:03,048 --> 00:59:05,248
<font color=#FFFF00>What a coincidence!</font>

870
00:59:06,388 --> 00:59:08,518
<font color=#FFFF00>She's very pretty, too.</font>

871
00:59:10,388 --> 00:59:13,588
<font color=#FFFF00>I need to meet her first.</font>

872
00:59:15,888 --> 00:59:16,948
<font color=#FFFF00>After that,</font>

873
00:59:17,488 --> 00:59:20,248
<font color=#FFFF00>I will sign the contract with her.</font>

874
00:59:21,588 --> 00:59:22,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Only then,</font>

875
00:59:23,248 --> 00:59:24,588
<font color=#FFFF00>I will get to see you...</font>

876
00:59:26,388 --> 00:59:29,118
<font color=#FFFF00>and your granddaughter for a long time.</font>

877
00:59:30,388 --> 00:59:31,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Take care then.</font>

878
00:59:56,188 --> 00:59:57,618
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you sleep well, Sir?</font>

879
01:00:00,488 --> 01:00:01,488
<font color=#FFFF00>No.</font>

880
01:00:02,718 --> 01:00:04,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it because of Jeong Eun?</font>

881
01:00:06,248 --> 01:00:07,588
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't want to talk about it.</font>

882
01:00:09,688 --> 01:00:11,748
<font color=#FFFF00>You should've slept well.</font>

883
01:00:15,848 --> 01:00:19,148
<font color=#FFFF00>Only then, you will get to...</font>

884
01:00:20,218 --> 01:00:22,648
<font color=#FFFF00>read the morning paper with a clear mind.</font>

885
01:00:28,518 --> 01:00:30,288
<font color=#FFFF00>(Jinsung Daily News)</font>

886
01:00:30,518 --> 01:00:32,487
<font color=#FFFF00>(Seonghan Group evades tax!)</font>

887
01:00:32,488 --> 01:00:35,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Han Seong Sik will start going down today.</font>

888
01:00:48,888 --> 01:00:50,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness.</font>

889
01:00:56,588 --> 01:00:59,388
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh, why are there so many things...</font>

890
01:00:59,518 --> 01:01:00,688
<font color=#FFFF00>happening to Seong Sik...</font>

891
01:01:01,548 --> 01:01:03,218
<font color=#FFFF00>and Dad?</font>

892
01:01:04,748 --> 01:01:06,018
<font color=#FFFF00>(Seonghan Group evades tax!)</font>

893
01:01:07,588 --> 01:01:08,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Seonghan Group?</font>

894
01:01:08,848 --> 01:01:10,287
<font color=#FFFF00>(Attorney H gives them
advice on avoiding tax.)</font>

895
01:01:10,288 --> 01:01:11,787
<font color=#FFFF00>(They sought to avoid the
prosecution investigation.)</font>

896
01:01:11,788 --> 01:01:14,428
<font color=#FFFF00>(They closed down their subsidiaries
without proper compensation.)</font>

897
01:01:26,548 --> 01:01:29,148
<font color=#FFFF00>(Seonghan Group, tax evasion
of Seonghan Group, Attorney H)</font>

898
01:01:41,018 --> 01:01:42,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Where are you?</font>

899
01:01:43,588 --> 01:01:46,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Where would I be? I'm at my office.</font>

900
01:01:46,788 --> 01:01:47,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Good thing you called.</font>

901
01:01:48,418 --> 01:01:50,587
<font color=#FFFF00>I've been busy all morning with
the women's society meeting...</font>

902
01:01:50,588 --> 01:01:53,018
<font color=#FFFF00>and the alpine club meeting.
And I'm starving now.</font>

903
01:01:53,288 --> 01:01:55,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Please cook me some chicken.</font>

904
01:01:55,388 --> 01:01:56,918
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll get half-and-half. I want
a lot of pickled radishes.</font>

905
01:01:57,188 --> 01:01:59,247
<font color=#FFFF00>It's not the time for fried chicken.</font>

906
01:01:59,248 --> 01:02:02,417
<font color=#FFFF00>Should I eat there? I guess
it will smell if I eat here.</font>

907
01:02:02,418 --> 01:02:03,588
<font color=#FFFF00>I will go down now. Okay?</font>

908
01:02:05,218 --> 01:02:07,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Hey, don't come. Don't come.</font>

909
01:02:07,618 --> 01:02:09,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Sik! Seong Sik!</font>

910
01:02:10,748 --> 01:02:12,118
<font color=#FFFF00>Gosh.</font>

911
01:02:15,048 --> 01:02:17,087
<font color=#FFFF00>The number you have dialed is
not available at this moment.</font>

912
01:02:17,088 --> 01:02:18,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Why aren't you picking up your phone?</font>

913
01:02:18,918 --> 01:02:19,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Hoon.</font>

914
01:02:20,988 --> 01:02:22,048
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it?</font>

915
01:02:22,218 --> 01:02:24,347
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on?</font>

916
01:02:24,348 --> 01:02:26,317
<font color=#FFFF00>Is it true that you provided
illegal advice to help...</font>

917
01:02:26,318 --> 01:02:28,088
<font color=#FFFF00>Seonghan Group evade tax?</font>

918
01:02:28,248 --> 01:02:31,687
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you Attorney H who got a
large sum of money for...</font>

919
01:02:31,688 --> 01:02:32,947
<font color=#FFFF00>providing the illegal advice?</font>

920
01:02:32,948 --> 01:02:35,617
<font color=#FFFF00>Did you get nominated as a reward?</font>

921
01:02:35,618 --> 01:02:36,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Sik! Seong Sik!</font>

922
01:02:37,118 --> 01:02:38,118
<font color=#FFFF00>- Seong Sik!
- Seong Hoon!</font>

923
01:02:38,119 --> 01:02:39,518
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on here?</font>

924
01:02:39,688 --> 01:02:40,918
<font color=#FFFF00>What's going on?</font>

925
01:02:41,018 --> 01:02:42,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Move!</font>

926
01:02:43,488 --> 01:02:44,618
<font color=#FFFF00>No! No!</font>

927
01:02:45,048 --> 01:02:46,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Cover your face.</font>

928
01:02:46,788 --> 01:02:48,017
<font color=#FFFF00>Please say something.</font>

929
01:02:48,018 --> 01:02:49,788
<font color=#FFFF00>- What's going on?
- Please say something.</font>

930
01:02:49,888 --> 01:02:50,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Move!</font>

931
01:02:52,848 --> 01:02:54,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Welcome.</font>

932
01:02:58,318 --> 01:02:59,318
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon.</font>

933
01:03:00,218 --> 01:03:01,288
<font color=#FFFF00>Here.</font>

934
01:03:13,488 --> 01:03:16,018
<font color=#FFFF00>I can't even recognize you now.</font>

935
01:03:16,348 --> 01:03:18,948
<font color=#FFFF00>You grew into a handsome man.</font>

936
01:03:26,818 --> 01:03:29,418
<font color=#FFFF00>You understand me well
because you are young.</font>

937
01:03:30,418 --> 01:03:31,618
<font color=#FFFF00>Take that...</font>

938
01:03:32,148 --> 01:03:34,948
<font color=#FFFF00>and don't bother my dad anymore.</font>

939
01:03:35,618 --> 01:03:37,848
<font color=#FFFF00>I never bothered him.</font>

940
01:03:38,948 --> 01:03:40,587
<font color=#FFFF00>Don't show up again.</font>

941
01:03:40,588 --> 01:03:42,888
<font color=#FFFF00>You are so mean.</font>

942
01:03:43,388 --> 01:03:44,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you know who I am?</font>

943
01:03:45,318 --> 01:03:46,518
<font color=#FFFF00>I don't care.</font>

944
01:03:47,148 --> 01:03:48,217
<font color=#FFFF00>What?</font>

945
01:03:48,218 --> 01:03:49,288
<font color=#FFFF00>I just want to...</font>

946
01:03:49,788 --> 01:03:52,188
<font color=#FFFF00>protect my dad.</font>

947
01:03:52,988 --> 01:03:56,888
<font color=#FFFF00>You want to protect your dad.</font>

948
01:03:57,348 --> 01:03:58,418
<font color=#FFFF00>Yes.</font>

949
01:03:58,818 --> 01:04:02,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Seong Joon, you are so naive.</font>

950
01:04:02,148 --> 01:04:03,648
<font color=#FFFF00>You're too nice.</font>

951
01:04:04,288 --> 01:04:08,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Goodness. What did he do to him?</font>

952
01:04:10,148 --> 01:04:11,948
<font color=#FFFF00>Do you really not remember anything?</font>

953
01:04:12,218 --> 01:04:14,148
<font color=#FFFF00>What is it that you want to say?</font>

954
01:04:14,618 --> 01:04:15,718
<font color=#FFFF00>All right.</font>

955
01:04:16,248 --> 01:04:18,048
<font color=#FFFF00>Since you gave me money,</font>

956
01:04:18,648 --> 01:04:21,088
<font color=#FFFF00>I will give you a crucial information.</font>

957
01:04:23,688 --> 01:04:25,248
<font color=#FFFF00>Your dad...</font>

958
01:04:26,218 --> 01:04:27,948
<font color=#FFFF00>is not your biological dad.</font>

959
01:04:28,648 --> 01:04:31,948
<font color=#FFFF00>He told the orphanage that he
is your biological father.</font>

960
01:04:34,388 --> 01:04:35,518
<font color=#FFFF00>But he is not.</font>

961
01:04:41,348 --> 01:04:43,048
<font color=#FFFF00>He's a silly man.</font>

962
01:04:44,048 --> 01:04:46,118
<font color=#FFFF00>He fooled you completely.</font>

963
01:04:47,848 --> 01:04:51,888
<font color=#FFFF00>I guess you needed to believe that
you were related to one of them.</font>

964
01:04:52,088 --> 01:04:54,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Only then, you would've
endured your time there.</font>

965
01:04:56,018 --> 01:04:57,048
<font color=#FFFF00>What...</font>

966
01:04:58,418 --> 01:04:59,948
<font color=#FFFF00>What are you saying?</font>

967
01:05:00,288 --> 01:05:01,818
<font color=#FFFF00>I'll tell you one more thing.</font>

968
01:05:03,418 --> 01:05:04,718
<font color=#FFFF00>You shouldn't...</font>

969
01:05:05,118 --> 01:05:07,048
<font color=#FFFF00>admire your father so much.</font>

970
01:05:07,848 --> 01:05:09,788
<font color=#FFFF00>He's...</font>

971
01:05:11,048 --> 01:05:12,148
<font color=#FFFF00>not so admirable after all.</font>

972
01:05:34,388 --> 01:05:36,218
<font color=#FFFF00>(Father, I'll Take Care of You)</font>

973
01:05:36,418 --> 01:05:38,888
<font color=#FFFF00>Dong Hui should be writing a script.</font>

974
01:05:38,988 --> 01:05:40,518
<font color=#FFFF00>I told her to come to the office.</font>

975
01:05:40,888 --> 01:05:42,417
<font color=#FFFF00>So why are they saying...</font>

976
01:05:42,418 --> 01:05:45,117
<font color=#FFFF00>that I provided illegal counsel
to help them evade tax?</font>

977
01:05:45,118 --> 01:05:47,117
<font color=#FFFF00>- You are mad!
- Honey!</font>

978
01:05:47,118 --> 01:05:49,218
<font color=#FFFF00>- I am divorcing you.
- Honey!</font>

979
01:05:50,248 --> 01:05:52,288
<font color=#FFFF00>If you don't want to see
Director Han lose his job,</font>

980
01:05:52,388 --> 01:05:54,488
<font color=#FFFF00>you should think carefully.</font>

981
01:05:54,918 --> 01:05:55,918
<font color=#FFFF00>Are you...</font>

982
01:05:56,388 --> 01:05:57,988
<font color=#FFFF00>my mother?</font>

983
01:05:58,488 --> 01:06:00,748
<font color=#FFFF00>Everything I believed is gone.</font>

984
01:06:00,918 --> 01:06:02,118
<font color=#FFFF00>It's killing me.</font>

